ong&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/style\"><code>&lt;style&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/sub\"><code>&lt;sub&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/summary\"><code>&lt;summary&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/sup\"><code>&lt;sup&gt;</code></a></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>T\n <ol>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/table\"><code>&lt;table&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/tbody\"><code>&lt;tbody&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/td\"><code>&lt;td&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li class=\"webcomp\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/template\"><code>&lt;template&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/textarea\"><code>&lt;textarea&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/tfoot\"><code>&lt;tfoot&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/th\"><code>&lt;th&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/thead\"><code>&lt;thead&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/time\"><code>&lt;time&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/title\"><code>&lt;title&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/tr\"><code>&lt;tr&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/track\"><code>&lt;track&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><s class=\"obsoleteElement\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/tt\"><code>&lt;tt&gt;</code></a></s></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>U\n <ol>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/u\"><code>&lt;u&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/ul\"><code>&lt;ul&gt;</code></a></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>V\n <ol>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/var\"><code>&lt;var&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/video\"><code>&lt;video&gt;</code></a></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>W\n <ol>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/wbr\"><code>&lt;wbr&gt;</code></a></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>X Y Z\n <ol>\n  <li><s class=\"obsoleteElement\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/xmp\"><code>&lt;xmp&gt;</code></a></s></li>\n </ol>\n    </li>\n   </ol>\n   </details></li>\n   </ol>\n  ","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"summary","title":"Summary","isH3":false,"content":"<p>\n  </p>\n  <strong>HTML</strong> 双向隔离元素 (** <code>&lt;bdi&gt;</code> **) 告诉浏览器的双向算法将其包含的文本与周围的文本隔离，当网站动态插入一些文本且不知道所插入文本的方向性时，此功能特别有用。\n<p></p><iframe class=\"interactive\" height=\"445\" src=\"https://interactive-examples.mdn.mozilla.net/pages/tabbed/bdi.html\" title=\"MDN Web Docs Interactive Example\" loading=\"lazy\"></iframe>\n<p>尽管同样的显示效果可以通过使用 CSS 规则 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/unicode-bidi\"><code>unicode-bidi</code></a>：隔离<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/span\"><code>&lt;span&gt;</code></a>或者其他文本格式化元素，但语义信息只能通过&lt;bdi&gt;元素传递。特别是，当浏览器允许忽略 CSS 样式时，在这种情况下，使用&lt;bdi&gt;仍然可以保证文本正确显示，而使用 CSS 样式来传递语义时就显得毫无用处。</p>\n<table class=\"properties\">\n  <tbody>\n    <tr>\n      <th scope=\"row\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Guide/HTML/Content_categories\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Content categories (en-US)</a></th>\n      <td><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Guide/HTML/Content_categories#flow_content\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Flow content (en-US)</a>, <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Guide/HTML/Content_categories#phrasing_content\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">phrasing content (en-US)</a>, palpable content.</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <th scope=\"row\">Permitted content</th>\n      <td><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Guide/HTML/Content_categories#phrasing_content\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Phrasing content (en-US)</a>.</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <th scope=\"row\">Tag omission</th>\n      <td>不允许，开始标签和结束标签都不能省略。</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <th scope=\"row\">Permitted parent elements</th>\n      <td>Any element that accepts <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Guide/HTML/Content_categories#phrasing_content\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">phrasing content (en-US)</a>.</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <th scope=\"row\">DOM interface</th>\n      <td><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/HTMLElement\"><code>HTMLElement</code></a></td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"属性","title":"属性","isH3":false,"content":"<a id=\"attr-dir\" href=\"#attr-dir\"><b><code>dir</code></b></a>\n<p>如同其他 HTML 元素一样，它包含<a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Global_attributes\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">全局属性 (en-US)</a>，但是有一些语义上的细微差别：<strong>dir</strong>属性不继承父元素。如果没有设置，默认值即为 auto，以便浏览器根据元素内容决定元素内容的方向。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"示例","title":"示例","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>p</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">dir</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>ltr<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>This arabic word <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>bdi</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>ARABIC_PLACEHOLDER<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>bdi</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span> is automatically displayed right-to-left.<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"结果","title":"结果","isH3":true,"content":"<p>This arabic word REDLOHECALP_CIBARA is automatically displayed right-to-left.</p>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"规范","id":"规范","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/text-level-semantics.html#the-bdi-element","title":"HTML Standard"}],"query":"html.elements.bdi"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"浏览器兼容","id":"浏览器兼容","isH3":false,"query":"html.elements.bdi","dataURL":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/bdi/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"参见","title":"参见","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n  <li>相关元素: <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/bdo\"><code>&lt;bdo&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li>相关属性: <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/direction\"><code>direction</code></a>, <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/unicode-bidi\"><code>unicode-bidi</code></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Summary","id":"summary"},{"text":"属性","id":"属性"},{"text":"示例","id":"示例"},{"text":"规范","id":"规范"},{"text":"浏览器兼容","id":"浏览器兼容"},{"text":"参见","id":"参见"}],"summary":"尽管同样的显示效果可以通过使用 CSS 规则 unicode-bidi：隔离<span>或者其他文本格式化元素，但语义信息只能通过<bdi>元素传递。特别是，当浏览器允许忽略 CSS 样式时，在这种情况下，使用<bdi>仍然可以保证文本正确显示，而使用 CSS 样式来传递语义时就显得毫无用处。","popularity":0.0003,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"<bdi>: The Bidirectional Isolate element","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"<bdi>","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"<bdi> : l'élément d'isolation bidirectionnelle","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"<bdi>: 書字方向分離要素","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"<bdi>","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"<bdi>","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/web/html/element/bdi","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/web/html/element/bdi/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/921c46a374ab0a9f4cc809af0370f8c412e54701","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web","title":"Web 开发技术"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML","title":"HTML（超文本标记语言）"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element","title":"HTML 元素参考"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/bdi","title":"<bdi>"}],"pageTitle":"<bdi> - HTML（超文本标记语言） | MDN","noIndexing":false}}